{"tid":807763,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我俾個女仔突然hea覆，死因何在...？","createTime":"2018-09-05T19:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T19:09:50.000Z","uid":185180,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9f1b84c35644046693619030e698d517ae462e74","tid":807763,"uid":185180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T19:34:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我早前想入一間銀行做<br />\n<br />\n喺討論區識到一個女仔<br />\n<br />\n因為佢係員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家都幾好傾，<br />\n<br />\n佢一直都會好多嘢講又成日都錄音，<br />\n<br />\n分享下工作經驗同面試秘訣<br />\n<br />\n有時一連覆成四五句<br />\n<br />\n又會鼓勵我搵工，同我講加油💪🏻<br />\n<br />\n最後我真係入咗佢間公司做<br />\n<br />\n大家真係第一次見面後<br />\n<br />\n我當然有多謝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但唔知點解由嗰時開始佢就覆少咗我好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾句變到半句<br />\n<br />\n甚至ok👌🏻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日我打咗一段野<br />\n<br />\n佢只係覆我「ha.yup」<br />\n<br />\n究竟有無人知點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd67a8b2f9629f4d826ce46f9bd50436ccfa8d3","tid":807763,"uid":185180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T19:36:38.000Z","msg":"點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ee80f8c16f78fe208f53f89c62b134877af15c","tid":807763,"uid":41139,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T19:37:05.000Z","msg":"見到個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1e709771de586c73b554d152d002cc3b33f45b","tid":807763,"uid":175598,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T19:37:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a883ce6d1a3df4de1ebbcd207a261469c664bf7","tid":807763,"uid":185180,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"dc1e709771de586c73b554d152d002cc3b33f45b","tid":807763,"uid":175598,"like":47,"dislike":0,"sc